      "span_text": "From these experiments, we conclude that overlapping rectangles are the primary source of difficulty for NGE and that BNGE was the best variant of NGE that we studied. Further experiments reported in [CITATION_1] show that BNGE commits most of its errors outside of all hyperrectangles."
